&control
    calculation = 'vc-relax'
    prefix = 'diamond'
    outdir = './outdir'
    pseudo_dir = './'
    etot_conv_thr = 1e-12
    forc_conv_thr = 1e-12

    nstep = 100
/
&system
    ibrav=2,
    celldm(1)=6.64245
    nat=2, ntyp=1,
    ecutwfc=80

    !add
    occupations='smearing'
    smearing='gauss'
    degauss=0.01
/
&electrons
    conv_thr=1e-12
/
&ions
    ion_dynamics='bfgs'
/
&cell
    !cell_dofree='ibrav'
    cell_dynamics='bfgs'
/

ATOMIC_SPECIES
  C  12.01078  C.upf

ATOMIC_POSITIONS crystal
  C  0.000000000000  0.000000000000  0.000000000000
  C  0.250000000000  0.250000000000  0.250000000000

K_POINTS (automatic)
 12 12 12 0 0 0

